---
import { withBase } from "../../lib/site";

const year = new Date().getUTCFullYear();
const links = [
  { label: "首页", href: withBase("/") },
  { label: "博客", href: withBase("/blog/") },
  { label: "关于", href: withBase("/about/") }
];
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <section class="footer-shell grunge-panel line-grid">
    <div class="footer-column">
      <p class="section-kicker">站点说明</p>
      <h2 class="display-title footer-title">写作、代码与发布放在同一处。</h2>
      <p class="body-copy">
        doriath 使用 Astro 静态构建，博客内容保存在
        <code>src/content/blog</code>，让写作记录和站点实现可以一起长期维护。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-columns">
      <div class="footer-column">
        <p class="section-kicker">导航</p>
        <ul class="footer-list">
          {links.map((link) => (
            <li>
              <a href={link.href} class="label-link">
                {link.label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-column">
        <p class="section-kicker">维护方式</p>
        <p class="body-copy">
          页面保留定制布局，文章继续使用 Markdown 和内容集合，部署逻辑仍兼容 GitHub
          Pages 与自定义域名。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="footer-meta">Jeffery Zhang {year}</p>
</footer>
